1. MySQL 8.x 설치 (Windows: MySQL Installer).
2. 설치 중 root 비밀번호 설정 (기억해두세요).
3. 설치 완료 후 MySQL 접속: mysql -u root -p
4. db 생성 :CREATE DATABASE hashbrown CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

5.가상환경
Windows (PowerShell)
cd D:\Project\backend
python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install "fastapi[all]" uvicorn sqlalchemy passlib[bcrypt] python-jose[cryptography] pydantic-settings

Windows (CMD)
cd D:\Project\backend
python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\activate.bat
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install "fastapi[all]" uvicorn sqlalchemy passlib[bcrypt] python-jose[cryptography] pydantic-settings


macOS / Linux
cd ./backend
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install "fastapi[all]" uvicorn sqlalchemy passlib[bcrypt] python-jose[cryptography] pydantic-settings


DB 연결 설정

app/database.py에서
DB_URL = os.getenv(
    "HASHBROWN_DB_URL",
    "mysql+pymysql://root:비밀번호입력@localhost:3306/hashbrown?charset=utf8mb4"
)


테이블 생성
cd backend
python -m app.create_db

테이블 삭제
python -m app.drop_db

MySQL에서 확인:
USE hashbrown;
SHOW TABLES;

백엔드 실행
uvicorn app.main:app --reload

초기 sql 삽입문
INSERT INTO interests (id, name) VALUES
  (1, '운동'),
  (2, '음식'),
  (3, '시험'),
  (4, '영화'),
  (5, '공부'),
  (6, '사진'),
  (7, '음악'),
  (8, '춤');
